{"tid":1101950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認串謀「呃保險」　黑警詹廣信求情稱父身體差母年邁盼輕判","createTime":"2019-04-11T11:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T13:56:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"199afd5e7c2dbc12497d8ac1ded8357308949db0","tid":1101950,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190411/s00001/6d439d45a0adcd0b4c365d92a9aa652d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190411%2Fs00001%2F6d439d45a0adcd0b4c365d92a9aa652d.jpg&h=ab2a42ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾任保險經紀的警員，被指控涉嫌多番教唆友人，甚至親自向6 間保險公司「呃保險」，意圖騙取共約18萬元保險賠償。兩人早前分別在東區裁判法院認罪，警員今日稱需時籌措賠償金額，獲裁判官批准保釋至本月16日（下周二）判刑。<br />\n<br />\n首被告警員詹廣信（36歲）承認11項串謀詐騙、企圖欺詐及欺詐罪。他沒有聘請代表律師，今親自求情稱父親身體欠佳，母親則年邁不宜照顧丈夫，希望法庭輕判，讓他繼續照顧家人。<br />\n<br />\n被告又承諾會賠償共約1.5萬元騙款，但需要一兩天籌措。裁判官批准被告繼續保釋，押後案件至下周二判刑。<br />\n<br />\n同案次被告曾憲楊（29歲）早前亦已承認共9項串謀詐騙、企圖欺詐及串謀虛報有人犯罪，正還押至本月18日（下周四）判刑。<br />\n<br />\n案情稱，首被告在2007年加入警隊前任職保險經紀，與次被告相識逾20年。在2015年，首被告建議次被告向保險公司虛報索償，將索償得益三分之一給他，由首被告負責填表，次被告則負責簽署索償，和到警署報假案宣稱財物失竊等。<br />\n<br />\n兩人其後多次合作，向中銀、三井住友及豐隆保險公司索償財物、家居及旅遊保險。3公司在公證行建議下拒作賠償。首被告更曾獨自騙取中銀及安達保險公司1.5萬元旅遊保險賠償。"},{"pid":"1914ae56b6dbfff57a19a8d2201ea4b72a4a41bc","tid":1101950,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"好仔唔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb21127d973f180330124ce16166403836a9aa3b","tid":1101950,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1914ae56b6dbfff57a19a8d2201ea4b72a4a41bc","tid":1101950,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"好仔唔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"男人黎講, 做黑警好過做保險"},{"pid":"b636456761a10afc469a7f1373cc8a8a1e4c8f3a","tid":1101950,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f41f432aa3b716594b3f04985db37cf92776686c","tid":1101950,"uid":121387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cb21127d973f180330124ce16166403836a9aa3b","tid":1101950,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1914ae56b6dbfff57a19a8d2201ea4b72a4a41bc","tid":1101950,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"好仔唔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"男人黎講, 做黑警好過做保險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"why not both?<br />\n香港四大賤業： 保險, 地產代理, 倫敦金同黑警"},{"pid":"be4fcf7bf86071870bececc1aec376c64bc7fdc8","tid":1101950,"uid":121387,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f41f432aa3b716594b3f04985db37cf92776686c","tid":1101950,"uid":121387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cb21127d973f180330124ce16166403836a9aa3b","tid":1101950,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1914ae56b6dbfff57a19a8d2201ea4b72a4a41bc","tid":1101950,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"好仔唔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"男人黎講, 做黑警好過做保險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"why not both?<br />\n香港四大賤業： 保險, 地產代理, 倫敦金同黑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"加埋傳銷, 5大至岩"},{"pid":"2f31d1eb28510d1f3a90009380230b5110691df7","tid":1101950,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:56:30.000Z","msg":"有邊個父母老左唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/b